---
publishDate: {{ Date }}
title: 'RSS Daily Digest: {{ Date }}'
url: /digest/{{ Date }}
---

{% for feed in Feeds -%}
### [{{ feed.Title }}]({{ feed.Link }})

{% for item in feed.Items -%}
- [{{ item.Title }}]({{ item.Link }})
{% if item.Summary -%}
  {{ item.Summary | strip_html | strip_newlines }}
{% elsif item.Content -%}
  {{ item.Content | strip_html | strip_newlines | truncate: 500 }}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% else -%}
_No feeds today!_
{% endfor %}
